OL,3,CJLR car sales recover after production
OL,4,Crestart following major cyber attack
OL,6,FCar giant JLR has revealed a recovery
OL,7,Fin sales over the past quarter after
OL,8,Frestarting production following the
OL,9,Fimpact of a major cyber attack.
OL,11,FThe UK's largest car manufacturer,
OL,12,Fwhich has a factory in Solihull, said
OL,13,Fit sold 95,300 vehicles to dealers in
OL,14,Fthe three months to March 31, surging
OL,15,F61.1% compared with the previous
OL,16,Fquarter.
OL,18,FRetail sales, meanwhile, increased by
OL,19,F16.2% to 92,700 vehicles compared with
OL,20,Fthe prior quarter.
