OL,3,CJLR car sales recover after production
OL,4,Crestart following major cyber attack
OL,6,FJLR, which is owned by India's Tata,
OL,7,Fwas forced to halt production across
OL,8,Fits UK factories for five weeks from
OL,9,FSeptember 1 last year due to a cyber-
OL,10,Fattack, weighing on sales in late 2025.
OL,12,FAll of the group's manufacturing sites
OL,13,Fstopped production but restarted in
OL,14,FOctober.
OL,16,FThe firm revealed it faced a #485m
OL,17,Floss, before tax and exceptional
OL,18,Fitems, for the three months to the end
OL,19,Fof September, compared with a profit
OL,20,Fof #398m for the same period a year
OL,21,Fago.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
