CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1775221865
OL,3,CJLR car sales recover after production
OL,4,Crestart following major cyber attack
OL,6,FIt said production is now at "normal
OL,7,Flevels" following the incident.
OL,9,FNevertheless, quarterly sales to
OL,10,Fdealers were still 14.5% lower than
OL,11,Fthe same quarter a year earlier, with
OL,12,Fa 23.1% drop in the UK.
OL,14,FIt linked the fall to disruption from
OL,15,Fthe cyber incident, the impact of US
OL,16,Ftariffs, market challenges in China
OL,17,Fand the planned wind-down of legacy
OL,18,FJaguar models.
