OL,3,CJLR car sales recover after production
OL,4,Crestart following major cyber attack
OL,6,FChinese sales tumbled by 29.8% amid
OL,7,Fcontinued struggles in the Chinese car
OL,8,Fmarket.
OL,10,FRetail sales were down 14.3% for the
OL,11,Fquarter year-on-year.
